blog.title: ℒ
blog.description:
》 MBLERGH, IT'S ME! 《
 Loki headcanons and fanfictions 
SUBMIT YOUR IDEAS!

body:
The Fight

“Hey can I request a fic where the reader and Loki are in a relationship but the get in a fight a huge fight Thor tries to get them back to talking with each other but it doesn’t work and when it does they have an amazing*wink* night. Thank you so much for writing the past request of mine it was absolutely lovely and I LOVED it. Thank you so much you are amazing.” - anon

After a little break imma slide into your feed again. But only for a short time. I probably won’t enough time in the future to upload regularly, yet I’ll try my best. I hope this one isn’t to disappointing haha anyway, let’s start!

-

“It’s our 10th anniversary! How could you possibly forget this date after 10 fucking years?!” You yelled at Loki, who has been looking at you with a resting bitch face for the past 15 minutes. Yes, he forgot the anniversary, but do such things really matter if yore happily together? He didn’t care about anniversaries much, or any special date at all. If you were happy, he was too. But forgetting your anniversary made you more angry than happy.

He sighed, turned around and left the room. You just let out all the anger by kicking the wall next to you until you couldn’t feel your foot anymore. Overwhelmed with rage tears started rolling down your cheeks. Maybe you were over exaggerating, but this was one of the little things that made you truly happy. And he just forgot it. Again. When Thor saw the both of you avoiding each other he knew what he had to do. He started talking to you, since you were the most hurt in this situation and started comforting you, telling you, that this is just the way Loki behaves and the way he is and that you should accept him, since he accepts you the way you are.

Then he rushed over to Loki and tried to get informations put of him. “It’s been 10 years, does she really think this is so special? I don’t get it. It’s just a number”, Loki said sighing. Thor put a hand on his brother shoulder. “You, brother, are a bigger idiot than I am one right now. It’s special to her. At least show her that you love her.” Loki looked at his brother with a raised eyebrow. “I would neve-” - “Pleasssse Loki!” - “Okay okay… ugh, do you know that I really despise you sometimes, brother?”

In the end, Loki couldn’t bring himself to apologize. It’s been 4 days and the two of you haven’t even looked at each other. You felt miserable and lonely and he felt anxious and rather lost. Neither knew what to do and kept avoiding the other party. But one sweet day, Thor had an idea. He prepared a bedroom for just the two of you and shoved you inside there, locking the door from outside. You looked at the door in confusion and noticed a note saying “I won’t let you out before you guys made up. - Thor”

Loki just sighed and ran his hand through his hair. “So”, he started after a while of awkward silence, “Are you still mad?” - “I’m not mad… I’m… disappointed… you know how much I love you and how much I relish being your wife. You forgetting the day we promised each other eternal love is just… hurtful.” Tears rose up again and you had a hard time holding up your composure. Loki, of course, noticed that and left out a big sigh, slowly coming closer to you. Before you even realized it he hugged you tightly and caressed your head. “My love, I didn’t mean to hurt you with such a small thing. I will try my best to remember that date. Okay?” - “And”, you asked, looking at him. “And… I love you.” - “No, that’s not what I meant. It starts with s and ends with y.” He let out another big sigh. “I’m sorry, my love…” - “Good boy…”, you giggled Nightly after saying that. It’s rare that he’s apologizing. Really rare. But now you had what you wanted: a submissive and apologizing Loki. “You know… You can make up for it~”, you said with a certain undertone Loki especially liked. Already knowing What You Wanted he lifted you up and dragged you to the bed, throwing you on it before he starting undressing himself.

“I know what my wife longs for”, he said with a dark voice and learned over you, starting to kiss you passionatly. His hands sneaked up your dress, caressing every centimeter of you body. He then started to undress you and pulled away to take a look at his beautiful wife. “I could really call myself a lucky bastard”, he said, licking his lips and leaning down to you again. He then proceeded to kiss down your body. You could say that this was a successful day, if you know what I mean ;)

-

-

-

summary: You’ve got a point, but by the other hand, I’m broke, and I believe you also don’t want me to starve, right? It might sound...
body:
You’ve got a point, but by the other hand, I’m broke, and I believe you also don’t want me to starve, right? It might sound weird, but hunting mystic food isn’t enough to keep my body alive and healthy. I need mystic food and human food.

And there’s no way I’m using my magic to steal.
